  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You install a mechanism to allow your Trick weapon to split into two weapons.</p><p> As bonus action, you can spend 5 chakra to split your Trick Weapon in two, granting you access to your Trick Weapon's base form and trick form at once.</p><p> You can revert your weapon back to normal on your turn (no action required).</p><p> For the duration, your Trick Weapon loses the Two-Handed and Heavy properties if it had them in either form, and you gain the benefits of Two-Weapon Fighting Stance.</p><p> While this Trick is active, you cannot use your Slayer's Rifle as you do not have a free hand to fire it.</p><p> Any additional tricks you possess are split between the two weapons.</p><p></p>",
